Subject: Friday in-bus entertainment

Without wanting to resurrect the in-car child entertainment
debate on-list, for all you bus volks with kids and who are
OK with the demise of old-time travelling pastimes like
conversation, games and enjoying the passing show out of the
windows, then it looks like you're in for a great ride. It
seems that the latest focus of all the consumer electronics
companies is in-car entertainment systems. The old bakelite
car radio has come a long way ...
http://www.wired.com/news/autotech/0,2554,61859,00.html

